33:15.341 --> 33:16.907
- What happened?

33:18.474 --> 33:19.998
- It's complicated.

33:20.041 --> 33:21.825
- Well, I want to know.

33:22.652 --> 33:24.002
- We...

33:27.657 --> 33:28.876
