33:34.186 --> 33:36.362
You see the way
she flaunts her goods.

33:36.405 --> 33:40.366
Well, the low cut blouses,
that tattoo of hers.

33:40.409 --> 33:43.412
I mean, it's a walking
billboard for...

33:44.109 --> 33:46.546
S-E-X.
- So you raped her?

33:46.589 --> 33:48.374
- No.
No.

33:49.244 --> 33:51.942
See, I feel like you're not
even listening to me, okay?

33:52.943 --> 33:54.075
[stammers]

33:54.119 --> 33:56.947
Annie--she's no...

33:58.123 --> 33:59.428
She's not like you.

33:59.472 --> 34:01.387
