like you.

34:01.430 --> 34:04.085
I mean, girls like that, they
want that kind of attention.

34:06.479 --> 34:07.958
- Rape?
- No.

34:10.831 --> 34:12.224
Just--

34:13.964 --> 34:15.183
The rough stuff.

34:15.227 --> 34:16.445
And, look,
there's a difference.

34:17.751 --> 34:19.405
You know me.
I'm a gentleman.

34:19.448 --> 34:23.104
But when a tease like that
pushes my buttons--

34:23.148 --> 34:24.584
and you know what button
I'm talking about--

34:24.627 --> 34:26.412
I'm apt to give her what
she came looking for.

34:26.455 --> 34:29.110
And I'm sorry if that's not
pretty or romantic,

34:29.154 --> 34:32.853
but it's human nature.
You know?

34:32.896 --> 34:34.463
It is science.

34:53.178 --> 34:54.962
- Do you have anything
you want to add?

34:55.005 --> 34:57.095
- You recorded me?

34:57.138 --> 34:58.487
Why would you do that?

34:58.531 --> 35:00.968
- I could ask you
the same thing.

35:01.011 --> 35:03.275
- That was before.

35:03.318 --> 35:04.798
- Before what?

35:04.841 --> 35:06.321
- Before I liked you.

35:09.063 --> 35:11.021
- I think you'd better go.

35:19.160 --> 35:21.031
- I want that back.

35:24.252 --> 35:26.515
- Just because you want
something doesn't give you

35:26.559 --> 35:28.343
the right to take it.

35:33.957 --> 35:35.524
[door slams]

35:39.049 --> 35:40.442
- Went old school.

35:40.486 --> 35:43.402
Cinnamon Schnapps.
- My personal favorite.

35:43.445 --> 35:45.882
That's like bat mitzvah
old school.

35:47.057 --> 35:49.886
- [sighs]
Sadie's almost that age.

35:51.279 --> 35:53.194
- Damn.

35:53.238 --> 35:55.370
We old.
- Dude.

36:00.506 --> 36:02.856
- She just looks so happy.
You know?

36:02.899 --> 36:04.205
- Just stop.

36:04.249 --> 36:06.338
- It was like there was this
whole other planet

36:06.381 --> 36:08.688
