months ago.

36:33.060 --> 36:35.236
Do you promise
you won't be a dick?

36:36.629 --> 36:38.457
- No.

36:38.500 --> 36:45.638
- Maybe I'm not the only person
who knows what's best for her.

36:47.770 --> 36:49.076
- I'm sorry.
Say that again.

36:49.119 --> 36:51.165
- Dick!
- I just wanna make sure

36:51.209 --> 36:52.993
