36:55.952 --> 36:58.085
- She needs you, too.

36:58.128 --> 37:00.218
Not the Schnapps.

37:00.261 --> 37:03.960
- That is literally exactly
what I needed to hear.

37:04.961 --> 37:06.311
Not the Schnapps.

37:08.574 --> 37:12.404
- Well, we just did in two
seconds what they pay lawyers

37:12.447 --> 37:15.189
for in blood.
- Leveled up.

37:15.233 --> 37:17.104
- Like some grown-ass folk.

37:17.147 --> 37:20.238
- Yeah, except grown-ass folk
don't use the term

37:20.281 --> 37:22.936
grown-ass folk.
- Hmm.

37:22.979 --> 37:23.937
True.

37:23.980 --> 37:26.940
[dramatic music]

37:26.983 --> 37:30.552
