money through this grocery

38:49.414 --> 38:52.373
store, and, uh, we wouldn't
even have known any of it

38:52.417 --> 38:55.507
if, uh, these two women hadn't
robbed the place

38:55.550 --> 38:57.987
a couple nights ago.

38:58.031 --> 39:00.338
- That's lucky.
- Hmm.

39:01.077 --> 39:02.557
- I don't think we should
leave her alone.

39:02.601 --> 39:04.733
- It's the same store Beth's
little sister works at.

39:07.562 --> 39:09.825
- Oh, my God.
Was she there?

39:13.176 --> 39:14.787
- That's how you're
gonna play this?

39:14.830 --> 39:17.311
- I mean, I haven't talked--
